546
00:44:37,550 --> 00:44:39,610
Hello, Hanamura?

547
00:44:43,360 --> 00:44:46,980
Farewell, Kai.

548
00:44:49,190 --> 00:44:53,210
Thank you for the delicious tamagoyaki.

549
00:44:55,760 --> 00:44:59,670
Thank you for the Napolitan.

550
00:45:03,030 --> 00:45:07,370
Thank you for doing the laundry.

551
00:45:29,270 --> 00:45:32,200
Thank you too, Shogun.

552
00:45:54,310 --> 00:45:58,100
Thank you, for everything.

553
00:45:59,380 --> 00:46:01,010
Yours truly, So Ha.

554
00:46:03,120 --> 00:46:05,030
- Hey, So Ha!
- So Ha!

555
00:46:05,030 --> 00:46:07,860
- How have you been?
- This... is instinct.

556
00:46:07,860 --> 00:46:10,160
I can't allow that in this office.
